:

1. On je često mislio na njegovoj* deci. (He often thought about his children.)
2. Svi su bili iznenađeni njegovoj* odluci. (Everyone was surprised by his decision.)
3. Njegovoj* majci nije bilo dobro. (His mother was not feeling well.)
4. Ona je pokazala njegovoj* sestri kako da radi to zadatak. (She showed his sister how to do that task.)
5. Njegovoj* brat je otišao u školu. (His brother went to school.)